{"word":"H502 - אָלַף - ʼâlaph - aw-lof' - Learn","slug":"H502","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָלַף</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼâlaph"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-lof'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Learn"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05DC;&#x05E3; - 'a&#x0302;laph</b> - <i>aw-lof'</i><p/>A primitive root, to <i>associate</i> with; hence to <i>learn</i> (and causatively to <i>teach</i>): - learn, teach, utter."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H441\">H441</a>, <a href=\"#/H504\">H504</a>"}]}